    "This adjustment helped make the chatbot more critical without dismissing the participants' ideas.",
    "The shared prompt was also improved between the experiments and included the names of the chatbot and the human, relevant project information, and the appropriate context of the conversation.",
    "We started with a generic prompt, \"Hi, I am your architect.",
    "Let us discuss your architecture project.",
    "I would like to know what kind of project you had in mind?\""
